		-- 1.3.6.1.4.1.8595.1.400.8.1
		cmCertUpdateFilepath OBJECT-TYPE
			SYNTAX OCTET STRING
			ACCESS read-write
			STATUS mandatory
			DESCRIPTION
				"The file path for CM certificates upgrade. The final full filename is 
				the path + CM_MAC_Address.enc. If the value for this OID is NULL, then 
				the default value AC698xNewCertificate is used.
				For example: if the value for OID is cm/certificates and CM MAC address
				is 009050abcdef, then the full filename is cm/certificates/009050abcdef.enc"
			::= { cmCertificateUpdate 1 }

		
